{[Os][pais][de][Einstein][,][por][não][serem][judeus][praticantes][,][não][se][importaram][que][o][filho][frequentasse][inclusive][a]<A href="/wiki/catequese" title="catequese">[catequese]</A></A>[,][que][agradou][bastante][a][Einstein][.&lt][;ref][name='Time'&gt][;Time][Magazine][:][\[]<A href="http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1607298,00.html">[http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1607298,00.html]</A></A><i>[Einstein][&amp][;][Faith]</i>[\]&lt][;/ref&gt][;][Curiosamente][Einstein][desenvolve][sozinho][uma][fervente]<A href="/wiki/fé" title="fé">[fé]</A></A>[judaica][e][passa][a][cumprir][os][rituais][judeus][incluindo][o]<A href="/wiki/Shabat" title="Shabat">[Shabat]</A></A>[e][a][comida]<A href="/wiki/kosher" title="kosher">[kosher]</A></A>[.]}
